00:49:55.580 --> 00:49:57.890 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Because they had
had the weather balloon

00:49:57.890 --> 00:49:59.150 align:middle line:90%
debris around.

00:49:59.150 --> 00:49:59.390 align:middle line:90%
>>HARRIS: Yes.

00:49:59.390 --> 00:50:01.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, actual
weather ball-- not this.

00:50:01.170 --> 00:50:02.128 align:middle line:90%
Actual weather balloon.

00:50:02.128 --> 00:50:04.530 align:middle line:84%
>>VALLEE: Well, the
property's 80,000 acres.

00:50:04.530 --> 00:50:05.330 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:50:05.330 --> 00:50:07.260 align:middle line:84%
>>VALLEE: So how many
weather balloons--

00:50:07.260 --> 00:50:08.060 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:50:08.060 --> 00:50:12.446 align:middle line:84%
>>VALLEE: The army was launching
weather balloons all day long

00:50:12.446 --> 00:50:13.670 align:middle line:90%
because of White Sands.

00:50:13.670 --> 00:50:14.880 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:50:14.880 --> 00:50:15.680 align:middle line:90%
>>VALLEE: And--

00:50:15.680 --> 00:50:17.210 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So they had
little pieces of that.

00:50:17.210 --> 00:50:18.500 align:middle line:84%
They go, we'll give
them back to you.

00:50:18.500 --> 00:50:20.917 align:middle line:84%
But that's nothing to do with
the avocado in our backyard.

00:50:20.917 --> 00:50:22.090 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHTER]

00:50:22.090 --> 00:50:22.890 align:middle line:90%


00:50:22.890 --> 00:50:25.670 align:middle line:84%
So the kids are going,
the father's going.

00:50:25.670 --> 00:50:27.380 align:middle line:84%
This comes in at
the last minute.

00:50:27.380 --> 00:50:28.970 align:middle line:84%
Sabrina comes in
at the last minute,

00:50:28.970 --> 00:50:30.428 align:middle line:84%
before you finish
the book, which--

00:50:30.428 --> 00:50:31.520 align:middle line:90%
>>HARRIS: In the 1950s.

00:50:31.520 --> 00:50:32.502 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:50:32.502 --> 00:50:33.335 align:middle line:90%
This was incredible.

00:50:33.335 --> 00:50:34.070 align:middle line:90%
>>HARRIS: The 1950s, right?

00:50:34.070 --> 00:50:34.430 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:50:34.430 --> 00:50:36.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And so
what do you think

00:50:36.170 --> 00:50:41.720 align:middle line:84%
that this pinkish, luminescent,
angel hair, spaghetti

00:50:41.720 --> 00:50:44.150 align:middle line:84%
stuff that they put on
their Christmas trees

00:50:44.150 --> 00:50:45.860 align:middle line:84%
and that stung when
she touched it,

00:50:45.860 --> 00:50:47.658 align:middle line:84%
bit her when she
touched it, what do

00:50:47.658 --> 00:50:48.950 align:middle line:90%
you think that might have been?

00:50:48.950 --> 00:50:51.970 align:middle line:90%


